g.text: Before register a Test, the Receptionist needs
to select the Clinical Analysis Laboratory where is
shows the Test Type list associated to the Clinical Analysis Laboratory and asks to select one
The variable "code" refers to the Test Type code.
[While the Receptionist wants to add Parameters to the Test]
shows the list of Parameter Categories associated with the Test Type
The variable "code" refers to the Parameter Category code.
[While the Receptionist wants to add Parameters associated with the Parameter Category that has been selected]
shows the list of Parameters associated with the Parameter Category
The variable "code" refers to the Parameter code.
When the Clinical Analysis Laboratory is selected (before the test registration)
the variable "clinicalAnalysisLaboratory" of the Controller (of the US04-ChooseLabSd.puml)
gets the value of the selected Laboratory.
As the Controller associated to this US is the same, then it is possible to do the step 45
because the variable "clinicalAnalysisLaboratory" is already instantiated.
